; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/spectacle.md

% spectacle, common

# Capture a screenshot of the entire desktop
spectacle

# Capture a screenshot of the active window
spectacle <__a___activewindow_>

# Capture a screenshot of a specific region
spectacle <__r___region_>

# Start another Spectacle instance so that you can screenshot Spectacle itself
spectacle <__i___new_instance_>
